# COMMON OS DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW CANONICAL

status: canonical
layer: development

## Workflow
1. Declare roadmap and current phase
2. Propose CommonOS change
3. Validate scope against domain-boundary rules
4. Review for reuse value and boundary safety
5. Implement additively
6. Verify against adoption targets
7. Publish updated canon

## Rule
CommonOS changes must improve shared reuse without stealing domain ownership.



